  "name": "Morrison CFD Hemolysis — VAD Credibility Package (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "This unit of assurance documents the credibility evidence for a CFD-based hemolysis prediction model applied to the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device operating conditions. The model has been applied in clinical research settings to inform device design decisions for Class III VAD submissions. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed across thirteen ASME V&V 40 credibility factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; six remain flagged as epistemic gaps at Model Risk Level 5. Despite these gaps, the overall credibility body is judged sufficient for the stated submission purpose under the Minimal profile, and the decision record reflects an Accepted outcome with conditions. No structured Context of Use object is provided; the intended-use scope is conveyed only through this narrative description.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-cfd-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-absolute-prediction-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-generic-centrifugal-pump-cfd-hemolysis-v2",
  "bindsDataset": [
