      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model input parameters characterized with probability distributions; Monte Carlo propagation yields output uncertainty bounds at 95% confidence.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated but only four of eleven uncertain input parameters were assigned distributions. Remaining parameters were fixed at nominal values. Input characterization is incomplete."
